FBIS4-38862 "drsov107_b_94018" FBIS-SOV-94-107 Daily Report 3 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military & Nuclear Issues Production of TU-160 Strategic Aircraft Discontinued Production of TU-160 Strategic Aircraft Discontinued LD0306083694 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 0730 GMT 3 Jun 94 LD0306083694 Moscow 2x2 Television Russian BFN [Text] The Gorbunov aviation production association in Kazan has discontinued production of missile-carrying strategic TU-160 aircraft, the POSTFAKTUM-AERO agency reports. Each of these aircraft cost several billion rubles. A number of them manufactured recently have not yet been paid for by the army and are still at the enterprise's premises.
